# Default Images Directory

Place your default slideshow images in this directory.
Supported formats: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .gif, .webp, .bmp

Images should be optimized for display:
- Recommended resolution: 1920x1080 or higher
- File size: Keep under 5MB for optimal loading
- Aspect ratio: 16:9 works best for most displays

Example files you might add:
- welcome.jpg (Welcome message)
- menu.png (Current menu or specials)
- events.jpg (Upcoming events)
- ambiance.jpg (Venue atmosphere shots)
